review_blob: Ok folks listen i understand all the bashing for domestic brew but come on, you cannot go from drinking a "rye loaf of bread" brew then drink a domestic beer and expect it to taste good!  This beer is one of the best domestic beers, sweet to the taste and a great finish.  If you like to drink beer that looks like motor oil please stop bashing "american" domestic beer!!!!!!!

Why this beer is so popular ill never know??????  This is the nastiest beer of the nasties!  From what ive been told this beer was once the bottom of the barel cheapest of cheap mexican brew that some guy bought, and poured money into marketing, so your paying big bucks for a cheap beer in an expensive package.  Funny thing is id much rather drink pbr, old mil, and milwaukees best any day over this nasty stuff.  If you want good mexican beer drink modelo, and pacifico...
Ok listen here if you are an American and are used to drinking American beer, how can you rate this beer bad?  When it comes to domestic "LITE" beer Miller lite is by far the best tasting!!!!!!!
